{
  "texts": [
    "Users must complete a task to reduce their anxiety or stress levels.",
    "Regarding the use of sensors, it is recommended to use HR wearable sensors, as they measure information on user physical activation, and can be combined with EDA.",
    "However, the use of EEG is rarely employed, although brain waves can be significantly affected in the case of phobias.",
    "Overall, the use of Desktop 6DOF or Standalone devices is recommended.",
    "The choice of these HMDs will depend on the need for sensor connections through a computer and the required capacity to run the applications."
  ]
}